subject: Figure Skating
lead_paragraph: Mao Asada fell on the opening jump of her free skate yesterday, but came back to beat Kimmie Meissner, the former world champion, and win the Trophee Bompard in Paris. Asada qualified for next month’s Grand Prix final in Turin, Italy.
